        {
          "text": "Your first-page style depends on how large your topic is. If it is large, it is better to split it into different content areas and have your first page as an overview and general process manual.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": { "id": null, "indent": 0 },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Always keep your instructions simple and readable in one sitting, so readers don’t get self-defeated by the whole document.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
